text: Suliman Sofyani (, born 2 February 1991) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays for Al-Sahel as a goalkeeper . ==Career== Sofyani began his career at youth Al-Shabab . left Al-Shabab and signed with Al-Kawkab on July 3, 2013 . left Al-Kawkab and signed with Al-Mujazzal on May 30, 2014 . left Al-Mujazzal and signed with Al-Faisaly on June 8, 2015 . left Al-Faisaly and signed with Al-Nojoom on July 16, 2017 . left Al-Nojoom and signed with Al-Mujazzal on July 16, 2018 . left Al-Mujazzal and signed with Al-Shoulla on January 22, 2019. left Al-Shoulla and signed with Al-Mujazzal on July 25, 2019. left Al-Mujazzal and signed with Al-Nojoom on January 19, 2020. left Al- Nojoom and signed with Al-Sahel on October 20, 2020. ==References== == External links == * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Saudi Arabia youth international footballers Category:Al-Shabab FC (Riyadh) players Category:Al-Kawkab FC players Category:Al-Mujazzal Club players Category:Al-Faisaly FC players Category:Al- Nojoom FC players Category:Al-Shoulla FC players Category:Al-Sahel FC players Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players Category:Association football goalkeepers
